HEADWORD: Gigantesque
<hw>Gi`gan*tesque"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[F.]</ety>
<def>Befitting a giant; bombastic; magniloquent.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The sort of mock-heroic <qex>gigantesque</qex>⟦br⟧
With which we bantered little Lilia first.</q>
<rj><qau>Tennyson.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Gigantic</ent>⟦br⟧
